Gregory P. Spivy
Partner 

GREGORY P. SPIVY is a Partner of ValueAct Capital. Mr. Spivy is a director of Armstrong World Industries, Inc. and the former chairman and director of Seitel Inc., the former chairman and director of MSD Performance, Inc. and a former director of Allison Transmission Holdings, Inc., KAR Auction Services, Inc., MDS, Inc., MSC Software Corp. and PRA International.  Prior to joining ValueAct Capital in September 2004, Mr. Spivy worked with Gryphon Investors, a private equity fund, and before Gryphon Investors was a Managing Director at Fremont Partners.  Prior to joining Fremont Partners, Mr. Spivy was a Director with The Bridgeford Group and began his career in the mergers and acquisitions department of Lehman Brothers. Mr. Spivy has a B.A. from Northwestern University.

